        <headline>Heat Advisory issued June 22 at 1:44PM EDT until June 24 at 8:00PM EDT by NWS Albany NY</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Heat index values up to 102 expected.

* WHERE...Western Schenectady, Montgomery, Southern Fulton, and
Southern Herkimer Counties.

* WHEN...From 11 AM Monday to 8 PM EDT Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
